Sauron - DNS/DHCP Management System
======


REQUIREMENTS
	- BIND v8 (or newer)
	- DHCP, dhcp v2.0 or newer from ISC  (optional)
	- Perl 5 or better
		- Net::Netmask module
		- Digest::MD5 module
		- Term::ReadKey module
	- PostgresSQL (or add support to your favorite db yourself :)
		- Pg perl module


TESTED PLATFORMS
	Linux
	Solaris



INSTALLATION
	.... (instructions to be added someday :)




SUGGESTED READING
	RFC: 952,953,974,1032,1034,1035,1123,1912


